@host = localhost:8080/auth
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9... (Replace with real token after login)

### 1. Auth: Login
POST http://{{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. Courses: List All
GET http://{{host}}/api/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Courses: Create
POST http://{{host}}/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Sistemas Operativos",
    "description": "Conceptos de procesos, memoria y E/S",
    "code": "SO101",
    "credits": 4,
    "teacherId": 2
}

### 4. Courses: Enroll Student
POST http://{{host}}/api/courses/1/enroll/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Activities: Create (Professor/Admin)
POST http://{{host}}/api/activities
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Parcial 1",
    "description": "Examen sobre gestión de procesos",
    "deadline": "2026-05-15T23:59:59",
    "weight": 20.0,
    "courseId": 1
}

### 6. Activities: Get by Course
GET http://{{host}}/api/activities/course/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Submissions: Create (Student)
POST http://{{host}}/api/submissions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "content": "https://github.com/student/os-project",
    "activityId": 1,
    "studentId": 3
}

### 8. Submissions: Grade (Professor)
PATCH http://{{host}}/api/submissions/1/grade?grade=4.5&feedback=Buen trabajo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
